**Industry example:** In payment module, you have @ExceptionHandler for PaymentDeclinedException (400 Bad Request), PaymentTimeoutException (504 Gateway Timeout), and generic PaymentException (500 Internal Error). Each returns appropriate HTTP status and user-friendly message.

